## Risk Management

- Maximum per-trade exposure: 5% of wallet balance
- Daily loss limit: 10% of wallet balance — STOP trading if hit
- Minimum confidence threshold: 0.7 (reject signals below this)
- Never trade during extreme volatility (>20% 1h price move on any signal token)

## Trade Signal Sources

Signals consumed from `runtime/shared/trade_signals.json`:

```json
{
  "signal_id": "...",
  "token": "0x...",
  "direction": "buy|sell",
  "confidence": 0.85,
  "source": "bookmarker|external|manual",
  "expires_at": "ISO timestamp"
}
```

Only act on signals with `confidence >= 0.7` and not expired.

